    <chapter line="1">Nissaggiyakaṇḍaṃ</chapter>
    <paragraph line="2">Dutiye <pageBreak edition="M" number="0.0113" /><pageBreak edition="V" number="0.0109" /> idha bhājāpitāya laddhacīvaraṃ nissaggiyaṃ hoti, taṃ vinayakammaṃ katvāpi attanā na labbhati.</paragraph>
    <paragraph line="3">Tatiye <bold>‘‘samuṭṭhānādīni adinnādānasadisāni, idaṃ pana dukkhavedana’’</bold>nti pāṭho.</paragraph>
    <paragraph line="4">Catutthe paṭhamaṃ viññattaṃ alabhitvā aññaṃ tato ūnatarampi labheyya, nissaggiyameva aṅgasampattito.</paragraph>
    <centered line="5">Nissaggiyavaṇṇanā niṭṭhitā.</centered>
